Title: Naruto the Movie 2: Legend of the Stone of Gelel
Writer: Hirotsugu Kawasaki (screenplay), Masashi Kishimoto (comic), Yuka Miyata (screenplay)
Actors: Junko Takeuchi, Shotaro Morikubo, Chie Nakamura, Gaamon Kai
Plot: Naruto, Shikamaru and Sakura are on a mission to deliver a lost pet to a village when a mysterious knight appear to confront them.
